{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Bring about a ban on smoking outside our nation\u2019s schools",
        "additional_details": "The health of our children is and should always be paramount\r\n \r\nPrevious law changes aimed to (a) reduce tobacco advertising (b) reduce the visibility of cigarettes and smoking products and (c) to protect our young people\r\nWe are long overdue banning smoking outside schools. Children are at times exposed to cigarettes and cigarette smoke on their way to school, outside and even in their playgrounds.\r\nThis is the least we can do to protect our young and impressionable from cigarettes and from smoke.",
        "background": "The Government should require local authorities to impose blanket no-smoking zones for 20 metres in all directions outside all our schools. ",
